<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,573,1102]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,328,766,792]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
The new subspecies differs from the nominotypic form in having a monochromatic back, without lateral bars continuing on the back. Lateral bars in most cases smaller and lower in number than in the nominate form, not bordered with white dots; lower lip is lighter than in 
<taxonomicName box="[1030,1233,844,869]" class="Reptilia" family="Scincidae" genus="Lepidothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="hinkeli" subSpecies="hinkeli">
<emphasis box="[1030,1233,844,869]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">L. hinkeli hinkeli</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and without any black markings on the first sublabial scales; body scales in most cases stronger keeled than in the nominate form.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,573,1102]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,355,959,985]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Colouration.</emphasis>
Throat and belly white, without any markings; dark framed light patches on the sides of the head between ear opening and forelimb, dark framing is lacking towards ventrally; laterally between the limbs there are eight to eleven dark stripes, not reaching the dorsal side of the body.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="15" lastPageNumber="16" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,573,1102]" box="[197,1382,1075,1102]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,254,1075,1101]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Size.</emphasis>
The maximum snout–vent length of the analysed specimens is 146.0 mm, average is 
<quantity box="[1257,1378,1076,1102]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.155" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" unit="mm" value="115.5">115.5 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<caption box="[151,977,1770,1794]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/186548/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" targetBox="[530,1057,1159,1744]" targetPageId="13">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,977,1770,1794]" box="[151,977,1770,1794]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
